rows.label: tlk41700222_01_msg0001
rows.name:
My name's Otto, and I'm the foreman
here at Nocclia Timber Site.

rows.label: tlk41700222_01_msg0002
rows.name:
We fell the trees here, and transport
the timber over to Saets Lumber Co.
in Trigo for processing.

rows.label: tlk41700222_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Then they can be used to make
furniture, musical instruments,
you name it.

rows.label: tlk41700222_01_msg0004
rows.name:
A lot of it also gets exported to
Superbia or Avaritia.

rows.label: tlk41700222_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Gulan wood's quality stuff, see.
It's sought-after all over Alst.
